wsdl:operation.name: login
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Log into the Mail Web Service. The userKey that is returned must be included as the 'userKey' parameter in subsequent method calls.

wsdl:operation.name: loginSingleSignon
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Single Signon into the Mail Web Service. The userKey that is returned must be included as the 'userKey' parameter in subsequent method calls.

wsdl:operation.name: loginStatus
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieve Login Status and/or Security Warnings.

wsdl:operation.name: logout
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Log out from the People Web Service.

wsdl:operation.name: lastServiceError
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieve the most recent IQMailService error/status message.

wsdl:operation.name: userMessageDefaults
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieves the user's preference settings for Message defaults.

wsdl:operation.name: assignMail
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Create a correspondence record for a person (as identified by peopleID). The return value is the Relation ID.

wsdl:operation.name: assignMail2
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Create a message record for a person (as identified by peopleID). Based on assignMail() but includes additional options for service ID and outgoing method. The return value is the Relation ID.

wsdl:operation.name: SendCustomEMail
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Send a custom E-mail for a person (as identified by peopleID). The return value is the Relation ID or 'ERROR details'.

wsdl:operation.name: attachIncomingMailFile
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Attach a file (in byte array format) to a mail record (as identified by Relation ID).

wsdl:operation.name: activeIQUsers
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieve list of active user IDs and names as object array.

wsdl:operation.name: GetWindowsIdentity
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieve Windows Credential Information.

wsdl:operation.name: incomingMethods
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieve list of active correspondence incoming methods as object array.

wsdl:operation.name: outgoingMethods
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieve list of active correspondence outgoing methods as object array.

wsdl:operation.name: issues
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieve list of active correspondence issues as object array.

wsdl:operation.name: getIncomingCountsByEntity
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieve Counts of Incomings for an Entity, i.e., State, County or Zipcode, as object array.

wsdl:operation.name: getIncomingCountsByEntityandIssue
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieve Counts of Incomings for an Entity, i.e., State, County or Zipcode, and its Issues as object array.

wsdl:operation.name: getMailRecord
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieve the mail record using the Relation ID.

wsdl:operation.name: getMailRecordByOutgoingID
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieve the mail record using the Outgoing ID.

wsdl:operation.name: pendingMailForPerson
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieve the pending mail record(s) for a person using the IQ people ID for the person. Returns a collection of mail records.

wsdl:operation.name: pendingMailForPersonPage
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieve a page of pending mail records for the specified person, where skip indicates the starting record (zero-based) and take indicates the number of records per page.

wsdl:operation.name: pendingMailForPersonCount
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieve the count of all pending mail records for the specified person.

wsdl:operation.name: ComputeDate
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieves a new date from the start date (leave blank to use the current date) adding to it the addDays value. The includeDays parameter can be: C=calendar days, B=business days, or S=IQ workflow setting for computing due dates.

wsdl:operation.name: GetCommonAnalyzeFields_JSON
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieve list of common analyze fields as a JSON Arraylist

wsdl:operation.name: GetCrosstabReportOnPendingMail_JSON
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieve Crosstab Report on Pending Mail as a JSON Hash Table

wsdl:operation.name: GetMailListID_JSON
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Creates a LIST ID of Mail as JSON

wsdl:operation.name: GetMailListRows_JSON
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Gets Rows of data from a Mail List ID as JSON
